ent-RMCWeaponBoltActionRifle-name = Basira-Armstrong bolt-action hunting rifle
ent-RMCWeaponBoltActionRifle-desc = Named after its eccentric designers, the Basira-Armstrong is a cheap but reliable civilian bolt-action rifle frequently found in the outer colonies. Despite its legally-mandated limited magazine capacity, its light weight and legendary accuracy makes it popular among hunters and competitive shooters.
ent-RMCMagazineRifleHunting-name = Basira-Armstrong magazine (6.5mm)
ent-RMCCartridgeBoltActionRifle-name = Cartridge (5.56x45)
ent-RMCCartridgeBoltActionRifle-desc = A Cartridge for the Basira-Armstrong hunting rifle. Compliant with the 15-cartridge limit on civilian hunting rifles.
